OL,3,CWelsh church launches 15-minute
OL,4,Cservices to attract more church-goers
OL,6,FWatch the video report from ITV Wales'
OL,7,FDean Thomas-Welch.
OL,9,FA vicar has become one of the first in
OL,10,Fthe UK to launch a 15-minute church
OL,11,Fservice in a bid to help busy people
OL,12,Ffit prayer into their day-to-day lives.
OL,14,FSt David's Church in Penllergaer, , is
OL,15,Fthought to be the first church in
OL,16,FWales to offer the speedy services.
OL,18,FThe Revd Dr John Gillibrand said the
OL,19,Fso-called "microservice" is being
OL,20,Fintroduced in response to the
OL,21,Fincreasing time pressures are facing.
