OL,3,CWelsh church launches 15-minute
OL,4,Cservices to attract more church-goers
OL,6,F"It will be no longer, no shorter than
OL,7,F15 minutes. It's so that people on the
OL,8,Fway home from work can call into
OL,9,Fchurch, find a space for peace and
OL,10,Fquiet and prayer and reflection, and
OL,11,Fthen go home to whatever challenges
OL,12,Fthey're facing."
OL,14,FIt comes as the number of Church in
OL,15,FWales members has dropped by 50,000 in
OL,16,Fthe past 25 years, with a #1million
OL,17,Fdrop in revenue reported due to the
OL,18,Fdwindling attendances.
