OL,3,CWelsh church launches 15-minute
OL,4,Cservices to attract more church-goers
OL,6,FThe Revd Gillbrand said he hopes the
OL,7,Fservices prove how the Church in Wales
OL,8,Fis prepared to innovate and "to face
OL,9,Fthe tricky problems".
OL,11,FHe added that the services aren't
OL,12,Fintended to be a replacement for
OL,13,FSunday morning services, but "a way of
OL,14,Fbeing in the church otherwise" within
OL,15,Fthe busy working week.
OL,17,FHe continued: "We're doing something
OL,18,Fdifferently, we're doing something
OL,19,Fnew."
