OL,3,CWelsh church launches 15-minute
OL,4,Cservices to attract more church-goers
OL,6,FThe Revd Gillbrand said churches need
OL,7,Fto find ways to serve the needs of
OL,8,Ftheir communities.
OL,10,FHe said: "Churches always need to be
OL,11,Falive to their context, to be thinking
OL,12,Fabout the context in which we are
OL,13,Fworking. If we don't, that's when we
OL,14,Fstart getting problems, because
OL,15,Fthere's this disconnect that comes
OL,16,Fbetween church and wider society."
OL,18,FThe 15-minute services will take place
OL,19,Fevery Monday at 4.45pm, starting on
OL,20,FApril 22, 2024.
